snippet.title: The Sword of Ditto - PS4 Gameplay Demo | E3 2017
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/the-swords-of-ditto-ps4/

Meet the adorable 2D hack-n-slash rogue-like The Sword of Ditto, coming to PS4. Check out the first extended gameplay, straight from the floor of E3 2017.
